Job Details
A reputed company in Abu Dhabi is looking for Accountant with excellent skills. Preferably Filipino nationality. Job Responsibilities Include1. Maintain/Monitor of Day to Day Accounts transactions (JV,AP,AR)
2. Candidate should be well versed with EXCEL.3. Candidate should have good communication skills – both written     & verbal.
4. Ledger Account Details & Reconciliations.5. Preparation of MIS reports for / to HOD
Knowledge of all relevant statutory compliances in UAE will be an added advantage Requirements Email: hrvacancyauh@gmail.com
Requirements
Commerce Graduates from a reputed University - Good Communication Skills  - Flexibility to work extended work hours. Ability to work under pressure. 2 years of Middle East Experience is a must.
